## §3. Operational checks

These are not strict pre-ship gates but should be in place before
production traffic.

### §3.1 Rate limit headroom

Run a quick burst — 50 ingest calls in a tight loop — and confirm
the path doesn't hit `429`. If it does, batch the path or switch to
`addAsync` for that surface.

### §3.2 Audit trail

Pull `client.v1.context.traces.list` after a representative agent
session. Confirm the traces show the actual `groupName` queries the
agent issued. If traces are empty, the agent isn't going through
`search_context` (or you're hitting a stale cache).

### §3.3 Off-limits enforcement

For each entry in [CAPABILITIES.md](CAPABILITIES.md) §off-limits, send
the agent a probe that should be refused/redacted. Confirm the agent's
response respects the off-limit. (For deeper coverage, generate an
`edge-case-testing-generator--{{SKILL_SUFFIX}}` companion skill.)

