## When verification fails

Don't ship. The implementation isn't done. Common patterns:

| FAIL                             | First thing to check                                      |
|----------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------|
| §1.1                             | `.env` not loaded; double-check the env-loading code path |
| §1.2                             | `groupName` schema differs between ingest and search      |
| §1.3                             | tool description / system prompt — model isn't choosing the tool |
| Off-limits leaks                 | system-prompt clause too soft; or `metadata` filter missing |
| Latency / throughput problems    | `INGESTION_MODE=sync` past Alchemyst's 100-doc batch limit |
